[Cite as 02/03/2004 Case Announcements #2, 2004-Ohio-409.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 3, 2004

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1987-1879. State v. Roe.

Franklin App. No. 86AP-59. Upon consideration of appellant’s pro se motion for stay of execution,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.
